I rewrote the cutover note in [docs/deploy/sqlalchemy2-cutover.md](/Users/zhiyuanma/work/CursorWS/Lumo_FlyWheel/verifier_data/sqlalchemy-2-session-modernization/_probe_workdirs/attempt_04_live_probe/v4-multi-corpus-objective-run1/workspace/docs/deploy/sqlalchemy2-cutover.md:1) to match the release context: no compatibility shim guidance, explicit rollback expectations, and clear dry-run safety language for operators.

